description:
The second collection of Handsome Flappy

From a total of 30 Handsome Flappy's & Steinschleudi's you get here the opportunity to be one of the first. Since there are only 10 pieces per collection, the number per buyer is limited to 1 NFT. When you mint a Handsome Steinschleudi NFT, you can mint one Handsome Flappy (#11-20) for free.

You can find the whole roadmap on my Homepage https://HandsomeFlappy.com

Within less than a month we have already collected over 900 Mi for a good cause. Be a part of the community and support non-profit organizations at the same time.

Have a great day, Hanna
name: Handsome Flappy #11-20
